  "narrative": {
    "text": "Peru is a Latin America and the Caribbean country with a DC-type pension system centred on the AFP Individual Accounts (SPP) \u2013 Mandatory DC. The system includes 2 schemes: AFP Individual Accounts (SPP) \u2013 Mandatory DC, Pensi\u00f3n 65 \u2013 Non-Contributory. The normal retirement age is 65 for both men and women. Contributions total 10.0% of insurable earnings (10.0% employee, 0.0% employer).",
